                                                <img class="c-image__img" src="/-/media/allianzgi/ap/taiwan/insights/weekly-report-tw/2021-11-18-3.png?rev=271cff7d3c5542748444331331fde465" srcset="/-/media/allianzgi/ap/taiwan/insights/weekly-report-tw/2021-11-18-3.png?w=640&amp;rev=271cff7d3c5542748444331331fde465&amp;hash=7F981F2C3B9FB4AD31DB4B5C4E8B96A1" alt="【股市資金觀測】美股資金進補 美中貿易談判正向" title="" />
